# God-file split drafts (2026-05-18 cleanup pass).
# These directories hold draft re-organisations of large source files
# (dxtrade.rs, burn_models.rs, training_orchestrator.rs, dqn_impl.rs,
# swarm_impl.rs, deep_models.rs). The active source files remain
# unchanged in the parent module; the drafts are activated one-at-a-time
# with a `Move-Item` after running `cargo check` per the docs/qa/
# `*_split_draft.md` activation recipes. Until activated they MUST NOT
# be tracked in git — they would shadow the real sources with double-
# compiled modules and break the build.
**/dxtrade_split_draft/
**/burn_models_split_draft/
**/training_orchestrator_split_draft/
**/dqn_impl_split_draft/
**/swarm_impl_split_draft/
**/deep_models_split_draft/

# Zero-byte sed-pipeline staging artifacts produced during the split
# extraction (see docs/qa/*-split-draft.md for context).
**/_section_*.body
dist/
